{"tid":1827064,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【政情】區選贏家民主黨　立會部署未敢進取","createTime":"2020-01-16T15:49:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T17:09:59.000Z","uid":164435,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"19782f3dda4b841aea1edd28746ba0d62ed8d6bd","tid":1827064,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T15:49:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=377018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D377018&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyotKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=40603f25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D377018&h=cc376083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=377018</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】民主派要在九月立法會選舉再下一城，要贏人，先要贏自己人。<br />\n<br />\n民主派第一大黨民主黨參選藍圖率先曝光，部署沒有大變動，五個地方選區各出一隊，超級區議會維持兩隊，現任議員全部爭取連任，只有九龍西黃碧雲面對深水埗區議員袁海文競爭。<br />\n<br />\n有「老鴿」向《政情》透露，民主黨在區議會選舉中贏得九十席後，黨內有強烈聲音應乘勝追擊，在立法會選舉中更進取，如新界東應考慮加派一張名單參選，但黨內最終決定以大局為重，以免泛民內耗而「攬炒」。<br />\n<br />\n民主派勢頭好，亦被視為是換代的良機。九龍西出現新舊相爭，黃碧雲接受《政情》查詢時指，公民黨、民協等多名有意在當區出選的都是年青一代，此時交捧袁海文，反而與其他民主派撞賣點，加上自己只當了兩屆議員，希望「再坐一會」，扶植更多區議會新人。<br />\n<br />\n黃碧雲及袁海文要在黨內初選出線，要視乎黨內投票及黨外的民調。《政情》聽聞，袁海文上屆初選在九龍西支部黨員的支持度，落後黃碧雲才無法出線，今屆再來挑戰會否加強信心？袁海文接受查詢時，只表示會努力爭取支持。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨初選提名期截止後，傳出東區區議員趙家賢有意出選區議會第一界別，他不評論傳聞，暫時專注區議會工作。有熟悉他的政界中人估計，趙家賢被咬甩耳殼後，知名度及支持度大增，或令他考慮爭取更上一層樓。<br />\n<br />\n不過，民主黨內普遍對消息感到驚訝。區議會第一議席首次落入民主派手中，民主黨雖是第一大黨，面對大量政治素人，相信也不會「話點就點」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qkmZDEa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqkmZDEa.jpg&h=f81d2ae7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59829e4a3a3b5756096a2f205ed8d0c8f27dd88c","tid":1827064,"uid":307619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T15:49:33.000Z","msg":"西九拍照被捕青年<span style=\"color: red;\">被扣足48 小時</span>  保釋金<span style=\"color: red;\">高達七千元</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1826845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1826845</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人今日唔出聲<br />\n呢種情況就會成為日常</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wKeoSjm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwKeoSjm.jpg&h=230579a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56543f252d2331ec85b7a72d9358eea35a91d0fe","tid":1827064,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T15:50:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">歐美議員講野又無人理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n響task2呀 幫手啦上唔到千呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyotKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=273aba2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"224618b3fb26ca356f193fa5c19df7c069f73744","tid":1827064,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T16:01:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6064239c30f7e40a1d10d177823e91e54f27de61","tid":1827064,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T16:20:36.000Z","msg":"Big雲邪神走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb80df753d2204bd5864199a70202800e5cf12e","tid":1827064,"uid":92002,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T16:23:00.000Z","msg":"在立法會選舉中更進取，如新界東應考慮加派一張名單參選，但黨內最終決定以大局為重，以免泛民內耗而「攬炒」。<br />\n<br />\n其實都算係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望有本土派出黎選 唔洗含"},{"pid":"5014bf2672fa513621a216d40e7a0194f94319de","tid":1827064,"uid":209390,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T16:23:47.000Z","msg":"算係百屌成材<br />\n除咗有一個女人賴死唔走"},{"pid":"312531daf4a46f57768cb2f3ff7277d64fc80eb0","tid":1827064,"uid":42629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T16:39:58.000Z","msg":"唔玩初選都得好難協調得好好"},{"pid":"a3817cce906b09618d3afeb7f9c48760c05d7d5f","tid":1827064,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T16:56:34.000Z","msg":"我唔要臭碧雲邪神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7385d88f6afb82719f0409ea307913826b4a390c","tid":1827064,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5014bf2672fa513621a216d40e7a0194f94319de","tid":1827064,"uid":209390,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T16:23:47.000Z","msg":"算係百屌成材<br />\n除咗有一個女人賴死唔走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T17:09:59.000Z","msg":"Big 雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}